{
  "stem": "16106.6",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then the school was full of people who were so-called [GERMAN], all sleeping on the floor, and then I got the runs-- then it worked.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I had all night to step on all those people, back and forth, and back and forth, and back and forth.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK, the next morning, I made my way back to the-- to this lovely family, the Poles, who came running out of the house, and kissing me, and hugging me, and being so happy, and they got to cook me a big feast, and everybody was surrounding me and applauding me, how smart I was.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one day, it was one day or two days, there came a [INAUDIBLE] or-- or a Jeep, or whatever those guys are driving-- the soldiers-- and said, is there a Fraulein Veronica [?",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Reimers ?] living?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That she is.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, I have to come with them, and I have a job to do for the-- for the-- for the Greeks-- for the Greek.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they-- I'll never forget this lovely lady.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She-- I didn't have a coat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She went to the closet, undid her good coat, her Sunday coat, which was an imitation fur.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Can you imagine what that cost in those days?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She had wrapped in papers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She lovingly unwrapped it and puts the coat around me-- that coat for the winter.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "What time of year was this?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was winter.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was January-- or what?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was the end-- it was December-- it couldn't have been.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was that type of-- time of year.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "At Danzig-- wow, was that cold-- I mean, snow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They gave me shoes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Those guys dressed-- dressed me up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, they had stuff for me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They dressed me up.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
